    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"37e90fe2\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Classification - Early Settlement: SAN vs SOL \\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"---\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Project Overview\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Objective:** Binary classification to distinguish between two types of early settlement:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `SAN (1)` - client settled the contract early on their own initiative\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `SOL (0)` - client settled on agreed time\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Data:** Aggregated dataset - 1 row per client, merged from 4 source tables:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"`BDOSSTOTAL` - `CRC` - `CredScore` - `FAMA`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"---\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Notebook Structure\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"```\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 0. SET UP                  Imports, constants, paths\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 1. LOAD DATASET            Load aggregated client dataset (1 row per client)\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 2. TRAIN / TEST SPLIT      Split once; drops 51 extra leaky features vs original  \\n\",\n",
    "    \"                            (FEATURES ARE STILL BEING DEFINED)\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 3. PREPROCESSING           Cleaning > Outliers > Imputation > OHE > Scaling\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 4. FIT & TRANSFORM         fit_transform(X_train), transform(X_test)\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 5. FEATURE SELECTION       Variance + correlation on X_train only \\n\",\n",
    "    \"                            (NOT COMPLETE)\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 6. MODEL COMPARISON        cross_validate: LR, RF, HistGBM\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 7. HYPERPARAMETER TUNING   RandomizedSearchCV on best model\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 8. FINAL EVALUATION        predict(X_test_fs), ROC-AUC, report, Confusion Matrix\\n\",\n",
    "    \" 9. FEATURE IMPORTANCE      Top-20 bar chart\\n\",\n",
    "    \"```\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"---\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Anti-Leakage Rules\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Rule | Where enforced |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|---|---|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `X_test` never influences any decision | Split in Section 2, only used in Section 8 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| All statistics learned from train fold only | `fit_transform` only on `X_train` in Section 4 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Feature selection criteria computed on train only | Section 5 uses `X_train_df` exclusively |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| CV uses only `X_train_fs` | Sections 6 and 7 never touch `X_test_fs` |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Post-settlement features removed | Section 2 drops 51 leaky features |\\n\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
