    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2. Train / Test Split\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"We define the target column and explicitly list every column that must be\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**dropped before modelling**.  Each is dropped for one of four reasons:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"1. **Target leakage** - features that encode partial or full knowledge of the outcome.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"2. **Identifiers / metadata** - columns that carry no predictive signal.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"3. **Raw date columns** - not suitable for tree-based models.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"4. **Post-settlement features (Phases 1 & 2)** - features aggregated from observations\\n\",\n",
    "    \"   using `'last'`/`'max'` that capture the state **after** settlement events, or\\n\",\n",
    "    \"   temporal FAMA/CRC aggregations that span the post-settlement timeline.\\n\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"187dbac8\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"execution\": {\n",
    "     \"iopub.execute_input\": \"2026-03-13T12:09:41.381750Z\",\n",
    "     \"iopub.status.busy\": \"2026-03-13T12:09:41.381551Z\",\n",
    "     \"iopub.status.idle\": \"2026-03-13T12:09:41.455291Z\",\n",
